            <lg xml:id="TK1136">
<l>maṭalūrtal yāmattu muḷḷuvēṉ maṉṟa</l>
<l>paṭalollā pētaikkeṉ kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Mine eyes will not close in sleep on your mistress's account; even at midnight will I think of mounting the palmyra horse.</l>
